fields.name: The Classic Barre with Extended Stretch
fields.description: The original serving of Barre, a mixed ability workout to tone and strengthen from head to toe. This workout utilises the isometric burn, delving deep into those intrinsic muscles and stabilisers. Just a few sessions you will see a noticeably improved posture, balance, and a lifted seat. ‘The Classic’ flows through high repetitions and low resistance, to improve muscular strength and overall tone. A flowing sequence of cleverly developed exercises, that leave you feeling stronger and leaner.

fields.name: Barre Flow
fields.description: A beautiful balance of yoga inspired flow to lengthen the muscles, weaved with a sculpting delve into some Barre based strength and conditioning. A class that focuses on the intelligent use of different planes of motion, deeper lengthening, stabilisation, balance and relaxation. Let go of the days stress, and find yourself in flow.

A class that focuses on the intelligent use of different planes of motion, deeper lengthening, stabilisation, balance and relaxation. Let go of the days stress, and find yourself in flow.

fields.name: The Barre Classic
fields.description: The original serving of Barre, a mixed ability workout to tone and strengthen from head to toe. This workout utilises the isometric burn, delving deep into those intrinsic muscles and stabilisers. Just a few sessions you will see a noticeably improved posture, balance, and a lifted seat. ‘The Classic’ flows through high repetitions and low resistance, to improve muscular strength and overall tone. A flowing sequence of cleverly developed exercises, that leave you feeling stronger and leaner.

Just a few sessions you will see a noticeably improved posture, balance, and a lifted seat. ‘The Classic’ flows through high repetitions and low resistance, to improve muscular strength and overall tone. A flowing sequence of cleverly developed exercises, that leave you feeling stronger and leaner.

This workout utilises the isometric burn, delving deep into those intrinsic muscles and stabilisers. Just a few sessions you will see a noticeably improved posture, balance, and a lifted seat. ‘The Classic’ flows through high repetitions and low resistance, to improve muscular strength and overall tone. A flowing sequence of cleverly developed exercises, that leave you feeling stronger and leaner.

fields.name: Mum and Baby Barre Classic
fields.description: Our Mum and Baby classes are specifically designed post-natal workouts to get you back into shape after giving birth - get ready to feel strong and regain a bit of you again! The Classic class is a dynamic, low impact, whole body barre workout with a focus on strenghtening your core safely with the close guidance of our instructors. Where possible please bring your litte one (pre walking/crawling) in carriers, so you don't miss a single snuggle or beat. Class is 40 Mins to ensure you get a great workout whilst keeping baby content. We recommend you have been signed off to exercise with a health professional before attending.
